headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Philinsure
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced it has acquired the remaining shares of Philippines-based Philpacific Insurance Brokers & Managers, Inc., dba Philinsure, following a minority investment in the business. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
